#COVID19 #vaccine Data for Ontario

As of 2021-01-28, #Ontario has administered 317,240 doses.

Based on a population of 14,730,000, it will take approx. another 3.90 years to administer to everyone in the Province. 

110,571 Vaccinations have been completed.
